title: Gananoque Dr Musallah
description: Huffadh needed for general Taraweeh (20 rakaats)
notes:
Gananoque Dr Musallah is a Ramadan-only Taraweeh training organization. We established this Musallah (2025/1446) to give Huffadh who normally don't get an opportunity at a large masjid a chance to lead.

Our aim is to provide a space for Huffadh to build confidence in leading salah and a flexible environment for those with busy schedules. Huffadh can sign up to lead any day or every day.

Great for new Huffadh, those with busy schedules, those who prefer leading a small congregation, or those who couldn't find a space in a masjid.

Requirements for acceptance:
1. Must have proper makharij and tajweed.
2. Memorization must be decent (able to revise a minimum of 2 pages with minimal mistakes).
3. Must be of good character.
4. Must be at least the minimum age for leading salah.
